.TH BT-JOY-CLIENT.SERVICE 8 "2026-05-18" "bt-joy 0.0.6" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
bt-joy-client.service \- systemd unit for the bt-joy joystick client
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bt-joy-client.service
runs the joystick client using
.IR /etc/bt-joy/client.yaml .
The service starts
.B /usr/bin/bt-joy
and restarts on failure.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B systemctl enable bt-joy-client.service
Enable the service at boot.
.TP
.B systemctl start bt-joy-client.service
Start the service.
.TP
.B journalctl -u bt-joy-client.service -f
Follow service logs.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/bt-joy/client.yaml
Client configuration.
.TP
.I /lib/systemd/system/bt-joy-client.service
Systemd unit file.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR bt-joy (1),
.BR bt-joy-client.yaml (5)
